Seven Injured in Multiple Vehicle Collision With Two Overturned at I-435 W & Holmes Rd, Kansas City, Missouri, 64131

11/7/2022, 8:28:09 AM

First responders received a 911 report of a vehicle collision with injuries.

11/7/2022, 7:34:09 AM

Further report states that multiple vehicles are involved in the collision. A vehicle is overturned in the collision. Reportedly, children are involved in the collision.

11/7/2022, 7:37:28 AM

Firefighters on the scene state that two vehicles are overturned due to the collision. They further advise that multiple vehicles are involved in the collision.

11/7/2022, 7:41:15 AM

Firefighters are requesting police to block the lane due to the collision. Additional EMS is being requested.

11/7/2022, 7:42:54 AM

Firefighters state that no one is trapped inside the vehicles involved in the collision.

11/7/2022, 7:44:50 AM

Six ambulances are en route to the collision.

11/7/2022, 7:45:51 AM

Police have arrived on the scene.

11/7/2022, 7:46:58 AM

Firefighters on the scene state that the whole lane on I-435 is blocked due to the collision.

11/7/2022, 7:48:57 AM

EMS on the scene are transporting one person to a nearby hospital.

11/7/2022, 8:03:20 AM

Officers on the scene advised that a total of seven people are injured due to the collision and have been transported to a nearby hospital.
